title: Sometimes Tom Hanks did not voice Woody from `Toy Story`
text:
Sometimes Tom Hanks did not voice Woody from `Toy Story` 
Entertainment Industry News.Net (ANI) : Friday 16th October, 2015 
Tom Hanks' brother Jim Hanks secretly voiced Woody from `Toy Story` whenever the Oscar winning actor was busy with other things. 
While chatting at a talk show with Graham Norton, who took out a Woody doll and asked Hanks if it was his voice, the actor said "No, it's my brother Jim," adding that there were so many computer games and video things, in which Jim worked all year long, The Independent reports. 
Jim Hanks is also an actor and has done a lot of Woody voicing over the years. 
Tom would be returning for `Toy Story 4,` which is scheduled to release on July 13 in 2018. (ANI) More Entertainment Industry News
